        {
            "id": "tag:reuters.com,2025:newsml_L4N3UG02X:0",
            "title": "Keurig Dr Pepper nears $18 billion deal for JDE Peet's, WSJ reports",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Keurig Dr Pepper </span><span> is close to a roughly $18 billion deal for European coffee company JDE Peet's </span><span>, the Wall Street Journal reported on Sunday, citing people familiar with the matter.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Reuters could not immediately verify the report. </span></p></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/reuters.com,2025:newsml_L4N3UG02X:0-keurig-dr-pepper-nears-18-billion-deal-for-jde-peet-s-wsj-reports/",
